data.description:
Perfect home for new home buyers, down sizers or any family. You will appreciate the improvements the home owner has completed since ownership. New roof, siding, windows, French doors, ac, furnace, bamboo flooring, refurbished hardwood floor, ceramic flooring, 
 all of the main floor bathroom, deck, drywalled lower level, installed bathroom, new dishwasher and fenced the back yard. Open living area with coat closet, and dining kitchen combination with appliances to stay, pass thru with breakfast bar, pantry, slider to the great back deck and fenced back yard. Two main floor bedrooms, plenty of closet space and full hall bath.  The full walk out  lower level offers a family room area with outside entrance & master bedroom suite with French doors, closet, master bath with shower,  laundry, plus more storage area. Located in a subdivision with 4 lakes for your enjoyment.  Owner in the process of moving remaining personal property from home. Schedule your appointment today!
